## Description {#details}

Two offsets pointing to a continuous substring.

End is not included, i.e. represents a half-open range.

Definition at line 57 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/testing/include/llvm/testing/annotations/annotations-h">Annotations.h</a>.
